room01.name: Landing Zone
room01.description: You land in a jungle. There is a path that leads north.

room02.name: Jungle Path
room02.description:
You arrive at a clearing, members of your team lie motionless on the ground, 
their parachutes never deployed. 
A well kept path leads North.
To the East, you see rubble and an opening in the ground.

room03.name: Jungle Clearing
room03.description:
You come across another clearing in the jungle. 
The path continues both North and South.

room04.name: Base of Temple
room04.description:
At the edge of the jungle lies an immense ancient temple. 
To the South lies a path back into the jungle. 
To the East are steps leading to the Temple.

room05.name: Pit of Face-Mugging Torment
room05.description:
You fall into a pit! Spikes stick out from the ground 
egg shaped pods are littered throughout 
and a dense fog hangs in the air. 
A door leads to the North.

room06.name: Central Chamber
room06.description:
You enter a musty and poorly lit room. 
Statues of lions sit poised in the corners. 
There are doors to North, East and South.

room07.name: Temple Entrance
room07.description:
You have entered a candle-lit room revealing strange markings...
"be careful not to disturb the dead." 
The temple exit lies to the West. A door is to the South.

room08.name: Temple Shrine Room
room08.description:
You have entered an alien shrine. 
The walls are decorated with murals of an advanced civilization. 
At the center is an alter. A beam of light shines down on it.

room09.name: Temple Store room
room09.description:
You enter what looks like a store room. 
Shelves line the walls where items were once stored. 
To the north is a door. 
To the South is a dark door with light emanating from it.

room10.name: Alien Communication Room
room10.description:
You found the communications room. 
A large metallic device sits in the center of the room.
a web of cables extend upward into the ceiling, 
allowing the device to send off world messages

alien guard.name: alien guard
alien guard.description: An Alien Guard leaps across the altar and braces itself for combat.

bald eagle.name: bald eagle
bald eagle.description: A Bald Eagle screams as it dives toward you!
bald eagle.success:
You fire off a shot into the sky, startling the majestic bald eagle. 
The eagle flies away and is no longer a threat.

cougar.name: cougar
cougar.description: A giant cougar jumps out from the jungle and attacks you!
cougar.success:
After everything you've been through, a cougar? 
Not even a challenge.

lion.name: lion
lion.description:
One of the statues has come to life! 
A ripped and shredded lion with a taste for intruders leaps into action.
lion.success:
You throw the ball O yarn at the lion.
It bats it around like a kitten. 
It's way too distracted to care about you now.

mummy.name: mummy
mummy.description:
Uh-oh, now you've done it. 
You have awakened an evil, vengeful, murderous mummy.
mummy.success:
The mummy bursts into flames immediately upon your attack. 
It gets reduced to a pile of ash.

face mugger.name: face mugger
face mugger.description:
A face-mugger tries to mug your face, attempting to wrap its 
creepy-crawly legs around your cranium. 
it obviously wants to re-arrange your lungs from your face!
face mugger.success:
You dodge the attack and kill the the face-mugger before it can latch on. 
No telling how terrible an experience that would have been

alien boss.name: alien boss
alien boss.description: A very large roided-out-extraterrestrial being stands at the center of the room! It screams something you can't make out,"^&@%# @&^#*(!( $^$#*(@!!!!"
alien boss.success:
Not taking any chances, you bludgeon the alien with the Crystal Femur! 
The alien leader is knocked unconscious.

anaconda.name: anaconda
anaconda.description: A giant Anaconda coils itself up, poised to strike at a moment's notice!
anaconda.success:
You quickly deal with the Anaconda before it can wrap itself around you. 
Injured, it slithers back into its hole.

communicator.name: communicator
communicator.description:
This is the communication device! 
I mean, imagine the technology these aliens have, man. 
Able to travel across the universe, talking with each other and stuff. 
Strangely, there is an outline that is the perfect shape of a femur. 
Theres also Some alien guy sleeping on the job
communicator.success:
You found a way to destroy the communication device, 
by carefully using the crystal femur to bash the console! 
You should probably start jogging to the landing zone before you get nuked! 
Also be careful of the alien you just woke up

pit.name: pit
pit.description: Ahhhhhh!! You have fallen into a black pit at least 10 feet deep!

locked door.name: locked door
locked door.success:
..Or is it? 
The door creaks open, revealing a dark and mysterious chamber beyond. 
The air is thick with the smell of metal and ozone. 
The walls are covered with alien ectoplasm, and strange markings.

desert eagle.name: desert eagle
desert eagle.description: The Mark XIX Desert Eagle is a gas-operated, semi-automatic pistol with a 7 round capacity. The gun measures 10.75” in length with a 6” barrel. Width is 1.25”, height 6.25” and the weight with an empty magazine is approximately 72 ounces. It has a trigger reach of 2.75” and a sight radius of 8.5” with the 6” barrel. - magnum research

grenade.name: grenade
grenade.description: A hand thrown explosive fragmentation grenade...

machete.name: machete
machete.description: It looks like this machete has seen better days. It looks rusty, has a bent blade and is missing a proper grip...

flamethrower.name: flamethrower
flamethrower.description: A sawed-off, hip operated, WWI era, five cylinder inert propellant (nitrogen gas) Flamethrower that is 90% spent. Capable of spitting a violent ball of Red Holy Fire in a 180 degree cone of fiery destruction... and it looks heavy...

key.name: key
key.description: Honestly, it looks like a typical house key... probably not that important.

crystal femur.name: crystal femur
crystal femur.description: It is painfully clear that this Amethyst Crystal Femur is shaped like a human femur, it is also painfully clear that these aliens must be cheap because Amethyst crystals are some of the cheapest crystals you can get in the market these days.

ball o yarn.name: ball o yarn
ball o yarn.description: An irresistible basketball-sized ball of yarn.

gameText.title: Temple Jog
gameText.intro:
The year is 20XX...

 A major government power has learned of an alien race that wants to invade
Earth and enslave the human race.
 They have discovered a secret alien ship that has been here for centuries.
 It has been disguised as a lost hidden temple the whole time!
 Their plan is to nuke the temple from orbit. As it's
"@|cyan The only way to be sure.|@"
 From intel gained, your special ops team has learned that even if the ship
is destroyed, a signal will still be sent to the alien home-world!
 Your mission, that you already chose to accept, is to:
@|bold,yellow    -Infiltrate the temple and gain access to the communication device.
    -Find a way to shut it down.
    -Get back to the landing zone for extraction before the bomb drops!
    -You have until sun-down at 18:00 local time.|@ 



 Press <Enter> to parachute into the LZ...
gameText.winText: YOU WIN: You managed to infiltrate the alien temple, disable the device and get out before the bomb dropped. As you look back from the helicopter, you see the nuke go off on the horizon. Earth has been spared!
gameText.sortOfWin: YOU (sort of) WIN: Earth commends you and is forever in your debt! You managed to thwart the alien threat! But unfortunately you did not get out in time to escape the nuke! You will be remembered...
gameText.outOfTime: GAME OVER: You were killed by the atomic bomb blast. The aliens were still able to send a signal home before the blast went off! Earth is DOOMED!
gameText.outOfLife: GAME OVER: You died trying to save the world, but failed. The aliens were still able to send a signal home before the atomic bomb dropped! Earth is DOOMED!
gameText.gameHelp: Objectives:                                                                       -Infiltrate the temple and gain access to the communication device.           -Find a way to shut it down.                                                  -Get back to the landing zone for extraction before the bomb drops!           -You have until sun-down at 18:00 local time.                                                                                                           Commands:                                                                         Go - Use 'go [direction]' command to move to designated direction             Look - Use 'look [item]' for item description                                 Get  - Use 'get [item]' command to obtain the item                            Use - Use 'use [item]' command to fight or kill enemy                         Sound - Use 'sound [on/off]' to turn on or off sound                          Quit - Use 'quit' command to exit out of the game
